m/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3506,3553,379718,388887],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ioo6hh/qi5oloEAMaCDk5MTEzOTczIJujtqYGMAA44QFABnIJNjE1NzUzMDE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"71 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-acf47adbd97932195c56b7fbc60a0dd5_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1732803533.475772","card_id":"Q_5290437318","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":5290437318,"title":"改变和接纳自己你选择哪个？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5290437318","type":"question","created":1732695027,"answer_count":49,"follower_count":57,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[14706,35034,380057,2254665],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"于我而言，改变与接纳的分野，就落在成为父亲这一身份转变的前后。 在闺女降临前，确切地说，在爱人孕期之前，我整个人透着一股“摆烂”劲儿。身材走样，工作虽尚可，但下班后便懒癌发作，诸事不想为，只求舒适安逸。即便如此，那时的我仍觉疲惫不堪，工作的劳累、夜晚的失眠与清晨的挣扎，仿佛无尽的循环。犹记儿时母亲的嗔怪：“整日躺在床上，难道不累吗？”原来，闲适过了头，亦是一种负累。 然而，自知晓将为人父的那一刻起，一切都悄然改变。从女儿呱呱坠地，到她牙牙学语唤出第一声“爸爸”，再到如今快满三岁，会对我提出各种要求：“爸爸，别抽烟”“爸爸，给我冲奶”“爸爸，抱抱”“爸爸，举高高”…在她成长的每一个阶段，我都不由自主地做出改变。奇妙的是，这些积极的改变带来的并非疲惫，而是身心的正向回馈。这便是我眼中，改变与接纳的分水岭——那个平凡却又无比特殊的“父亲”身份。"},"attached_info":"CkAIoo6hh/qi5oloEAMaCTExMjAzNDU1MiDzp5u6BjAAODlAB3IKNTI5MDQzNzMxOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"62 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-bd8fb78858bb16f5d748b0be2dbcd8d1_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1732803533.476630","card_id":"Q_5369542663","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2